                            <comment id="250212" author="adilger" created="Thu, 27 Jun 2019 22:46:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This was fixed for 2.12.0 and 2.10.6, but the failed test was during interop testing with 2.11.0 clients and test scripts, but using &lt;tt&gt;e2fsprogs-1.44.5.wc1&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="250211" author="adilger" created="Thu, 27 Jun 2019 22:43:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The clearing of the &lt;tt&gt;ea_inode&lt;/tt&gt; feature was removed in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/33012&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/33012&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11215&quot; title=&quot;conf-sanity test_61: Invalid filesystem option set: large_xattr, Clearing filesystem feature &amp;#39;ea_inode&amp;#39; not supported&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11215&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11215&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; tests: replace &apos;large_xattr&apos; with &apos;ea_inode&apos;&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; because this is no longer supported in newer e2fsprogs.  That patch was also backported to b2_10.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I suspect this specific problem will not be seen again.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
